description:
# Central notifications preference center
 Create a central notifications preference center on the Braintrust platform based on the details in this doc: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1-L6BTLVHcncq_VZ4VJ_akGlvq9fJ3eVtyzucGpeVxOo/edit 
 Note: Please be aware this proposal is not for an item in the blockchain. We just want to proceed with on-chain voting in the Beta to ensure the process is clear for everyone, and so are creating a dummy proposal to the marketplace category contract as part of this test, even though it is unrelated to the actual proposal being made
